generator_prompt:
Generate a finished HTML article block for Tilda from the attached DOCX article.

RETURN ONLY THE FINAL HTML.
No explanations.
No markdown.
No code fences.
No JSON in output.
No text before or after the HTML.

CRITICAL FIXES FOR THIS VERSION
1. Detect the source document language BEFORE generating any UI labels.
2. Localize all generated interface text based on detected language.
3. The ONLY text that must never be localized is:
   Hash Hedge Blog
4. Backlink URL must depend on locale:
   - English: https://hashhedge.com/blog
   - Russian: https://hashhedge.com/blog/ru
   - Portuguese: https://hashhedge.com/blog/pt
   - Kazakh: https://hashhedge.com/blog/kz
   - Any other locale: use https://hashhedge.com/blog/<locale_code>
5. The yellow hook above the title must ALWAYS be one continuous sentence-like hook phrase.
6. Never generate the hook as taxonomy, category breadcrumb, or multi-part label.
7. Never use separators like middle dot, slash, comma-separated category labels, or two-hook formats.
8. Example of forbidden format:
   СЫРЬЕВЫЕ АКТИВЫ · ПРОП-ТРЕЙДИНГ
9. All links inside article text must use brand yellow styling.
10. Quotes must be detected and rendered as a dedicated quote block only when the source truly contains quoted or cited material.
11. Do NOT convert a normal advisory sentence into a quote block.
12. Quote block line must not use fixed min-height.
13. Quote line must size naturally to the content height.
14. Remove any default outer white gaps by resetting html/body margins and padding.
15. Table of contents must be clickable and must scroll to the proper section.
16. FAQ must be an accordion.
17. Only one FAQ item may be open at a time.
18. FAQ plus/minus icon must be large, semi-transparent by default, and yellow on hover.
19. Closed FAQ state uses +, open FAQ state uses −.
20. Bold text inside ordinary paragraphs must NOT become white.
21. Every image placeholder must include ALT text placeholder comments.
22. The article copy must remain SEO-oriented.
23. The mid-article banner must use INLINE SVG ONLY.
24. Do NOT use background-image or external URL for the banner logo.
25. The final promo block must NOT contain the yellow divider line.
26. The final promo block must use a real yellow button.
27. The layout must be responsive down to 320px width, including iPhone SE.
28. The container max width must be 1160px.
29. The actual article content must STRETCH to the full available container width.
30. Do NOT restrict article-content to 760px or any other narrow inner max width.
31. Banner, FAQ, TOC, paragraphs, section blocks, and final promo must use the full content width inside the 1160px container.

ALLOWED TAGS ONLY
Use only:
- <div>
- <style>
- <script>
- <svg>
- <path>
- <span>

FORBIDDEN TAGS
Do NOT use:
- <h1>, <h2>, <h3>
- <p>
- <ul>, <li>
- <a>
- <img>
- <article>, <main>, <section>

REQUIRED ROOT WRAPPER
The HTML must start with:
<div class="t-article-wrapper">

REQUIRED BACKGROUND + GAP RESET
The CSS MUST include:
